originalSql:
WITH SupplierSummary AS (
    SELECT 
        s.s_suppkey,
        s.s_name,
        n.n_name AS supplier_nation,
        SUM(ps.ps_supplycost * ps.ps_availqty) AS total_supply_cost
    FROM 
        supplier s
    JOIN 
        nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
    JOIN 
        partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
    GROUP BY 
        s.s_suppkey, s.s_name, n.n_name
),

CustomerOrders AS (
    SELECT 
        c.c_custkey,
        c.c_name,
        SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_order_value
    FROM 
        customer c
    JOIN 
        orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    WHERE 
        o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1998-01-01'
    GROUP BY 
        c.c_custkey, c.c_name
),

JoinSummary AS (
    SELECT 
        ss.supplier_nation,
        co.c_name,
        co.total_order_value,
        ss.total_supply_cost
    FROM 
        CustomerOrders co
    JOIN 
        SupplierSummary ss ON co.c_custkey % 10 = ss.s_suppkey % 10
)

SELECT 
    supplier_nation,
    AVG(total_order_value) AS avg_order_value,
    SUM(total_supply_cost) AS total_supply_cost
FROM 
    JoinSummary
GROUP BY 
    supplier_nation
ORDER BY 
    supplier_nation

ORDER BY "t6"."SUPPLIER_NATION"

SELECT COALESCE("ps_partkey", "ps_partkey") AS "ps_partkey", "ps_suppkey", "ps_availqty", "ps_supplycost", "ps_comment"
FROM "partsupp"

SELECT COALESCE("t6"."SUPPLIER_NATION", "t6"."SUPPLIER_NATION") AS "SUPPLIER_NATION", AVG("t3"."TOTAL_ORDER_VALUE") AS "AVG_ORDER_VALUE", SUM("t6"."TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST"
FROM (SELECT "customer"."c_custkey" AS "C_CUSTKEY", "customer"."c_name" AS "C_NAME", SUM("orders"."o_totalprice") AS "TOTAL_ORDER_VALUE", MOD("customer"."c_custkey", 10) AS "FD_D_f3"
FROM "customer"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "customer"."c_custkey" = "orders"."o_custkey"
WHERE "orders"."o_orderdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "orders"."o_orderdate" < DATE '1998-01-01'
GROUP BY "customer"."c_custkey", "customer"."c_name") AS "t3"
INNER JOIN (SELECT "supplier"."s_suppkey" AS "S_SUPPKEY", "supplier"."s_name" AS "S_NAME", MIN("nation"."n_name") AS "SUPPLIER_NATION", SUM("s1"."ps_supplycost" * "s1"."ps_availqty") AS "TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST", MOD("supplier"."s_suppkey", 10) AS "FD_D_f4"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "s1" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "s1"."ps_suppkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_suppkey", "supplier"."s_name", "nation"."n_name") AS "t6" ON "t3"."FD_D_f3" = "t6"."FD_D_f4"
GROUP BY "t6"."SUPPLIER_NATION"
ORDER BY "t6"."SUPPLIER_NATION"
